logicalColumns.name: Service lines Amount
logicalColumns.description: Stores the amount on the shipments for service lines

logicalColumns.name: Service lines Amount Billed
logicalColumns.description: Stores the amount billed for service lines

logicalColumns.name: Service lines Amount Financed
logicalColumns.description: For Advances or Financing Pay Items, the amount which has been pre-paid

logicalColumns.name: Past Hold Period
logicalColumns.description: Total number of days this shipment line was with shipment_acceptance_hold_flag ='Y' (not including current HOLD period)

physicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 = 81 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) IN (4, 5) THEN %2 + 3.99999 WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 6 THEN %2 + 2.99999 ELSE %2 + 1.99999 END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) IN (5, 6) THEN %2 + 3.99999 WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 7 THEN %2 + 2.99999 ELSE %2 + 1.99999 END  END

logicalColumns.name: Shipment Acceptance Hold Flag
logicalColumns.description:
"Y" - If this type of acceptance represent vendor hold.
Else - "N"

logicalColumns.name: Shipment Last Acceptance Date
logicalColumns.description: Save the last time shipment_acceptance_code (ATTRIBUTE8) has changed

logicalColumns.name: Current Hold Period
logicalColumns.description: If Current Acceptance is HOLD - counts the number of days in current hold period.

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 = 'Y' THEN  TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , %2,  CURRENT_DATE ) ELSE 0 END
expressionObjects: logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Purchasing Po Shipment.Shipment Acceptance Hold Flag
logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Purchasing Po Shipment.Shipment Last Acceptance Date
logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Purchasing Po Shipment.Current Hold Period
logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Purchasing Po Shipment.Past Hold Period
